"Word Guesser!" >> Display.
"poppop" >> target.
"" >> guessed.

new Loop:
    "Guess a letter (or 'quit'): " >> Input >> guess.
    guess >> check:
        is "quit":
            "Bye!" >> Display.
        else:
            guess >+> guessed.
            "You guessed: " >+> guessed >> Display.
            null >> Loop.
    ..
..

null >> Loop.
